**Project Context (Project "Beacon"):**
This is a secure, anonymous, and empathetic multi-agent AI chatbot interfac=
e designed to support individuals struggling with substance abuse. The inte=
rface acts as a 24/7 digital first-responder. It must feel zero-judgmental,=
 calming, and deeply modern.=20

**Architecture &amp; Layout:**
Implement a "Single Pane of Glass" architecture. There are no page reloads,=
 external navigation menus, or login screens. The entire user journey happe=
ns within one central chat interface.=20

**Visual Language (Glassmorphism &amp; Textured Serenity):**
*   **Background:** Create a full-viewport, slow-moving fluid mesh gradient=
