the blur and border brightness.
5.  **Input Dock:** Fixed at the bottom of the glass vessel. A dark translu=
cent background containing an expanding textarea, a microphone icon button =
(Voice-to-Text), and a send arrow button.

**State Management &amp; Interactions:**
*   Ensure all hover states feel tactile and responsive.
*   Include a simulated "Loading State" at the bottom of the message stream=
