2.  **Input Dock:** Fixed at the bottom of the glass vessel. A dark translu=
cent background containing an expanding textarea, a metallic microphone ico=
n button (Voice-to-Text), and a send arrow button.

**The Chat Stream &amp; "In-Stream Onboarding" (CRITICAL STATE):**
